{"tid":1634767,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急！想贏嘅入嚟！！！","createTime":"2019-10-07T09:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T15:50:07.000Z","uid":204615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2de33c5e56269370c184c333c784c3aa0a0b20f9","tid":1634767,"uid":204615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:55:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">有D長，但麻煩睇晒佢。</span><br />\n<br />\n由6月至今已經四個月，我地由開頭只圍繞香港本土，到後來積極發展唔同戰線，為呢個反送中運動不斷帶嚟希望，成個過程真係好辛苦，好唔容易！<br />\n<br />\n我唔會話我地「就輸」或者點，因為呢個運動每秒在變，冇野係話得埋嘅。但想贏我地就要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">留意細節</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1.文宣</span><br />\n<br />\n我地嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣工作唔可以只係流於本土，甚至只係Facebook, 連登呢D同溫層！</span></span>Lennon Wall ， Airdrop 大法係有一定作用，但其實唔夠！(Airdrop 大法其實唔係好多人用）因為有好多人根本唔會睇唔會收，Lennon Wall 對佢地嚟講只係是非之地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">建議1</span>：文宣遍地開花，大家(尤其係和理飛)搭車坐窗口位，可以係窗邊放置文宣。令每部巴士都成為<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">流動Lennon Wall</span></span>.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">建議2</span>: 就算唔係坐窗口位，都可以<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係位放低張文宣俾下一手</span></span>，就好似外國會有人將自己睇完嘅報紙放低俾下一手睇一樣。咁當然，<span style=\"color: red;\">坐一程車冇話規定只可以坐一個位</span>嘅。<br />\n<br />\n宜家對國際嘅文宣係好唔足夠，好多外國人對我地發生嘅事係一知半解，甚至故意抹黑！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">建議3</span>: <span style=\"color: red;\">唔好淨係自己tweet 同放hashtag</span>。行多步，click 入D hashtag，你會發現有好多外國人post 緊D fake news，完全係外國版藍絲五毛。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係佢地嘅tweet 下面有禮貌地留言，貼文宣！</span></span>令睇到佢地個tweet 嘅人都睇到真相！<br />\n<br />\n外國人睇到佢地本土嘅人Twitter 機會率係高過睇到我地嘅好多。佢地有自己嘅朋友，咁做嘅目標係要正視聽，at least 阻止更多外國人由乜都唔知，睇吓睇吓退化成為藍絲<span style=\"color: blue;\">。<br />\n記住，外國人先係高官議員嘅選民，要得到外國人大多數支持，國際戰線先可以延續</span>。<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔可以俾佢地以為我地係無差別攻擊商鋪</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 緊急法 </span><br />\n<br />\n個人認為 777條仆街短期內再用緊急法係相當有可能！我地成場運動主要係靠乜嚟通訊同組織大家都清楚。如果冇咗internet 係好難搞，但唔係冇方法！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">建議4</span>: Download <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Bridgefy</span></span>. 佢係利用藍芽組成網絡，只要夠多人download 同用，理論上係可以好似突破地域嘅限制，而唔需要靠data/ WiFi。就算777唔全港斷網，我地去到人多/收得唔好嘅地方，都可以用佢黎聯絡甚至boardcast. <br />\n(<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">壞處</span></span>係要用電話號碼登記，變相好似<span style=\"color: green;\">whatsapp</span> 咁，而唔係telegram。但可以斷網時緊急嘅代替品）<br />\n<br />\n(iOS 版 App Store 網址：<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/app/bridgefy/id975776347\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fapp%2Fbridgefy%2Fid975776347&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn0igq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=56070fbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/app/bridgefy/id975776347</a><br />\nAndroid 版 Google Play 網址：<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=me.bridgefy.main\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dme.bridgefy.main&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn0igq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=f56d3c44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=me.bridgefy.main</a> )<br />\n<br />\n呢篇野唔係我寫，但個人認為好值得睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2342353579362317&amp;id=1432983410299343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2342353579362317%26id%3D1432983410299343&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn0igq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=83ab6052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2342353579362317&amp;id=1432983410299343</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎改位提出意見、改進方法，但唔好齋屌。<br />\n<br />\n利申：非IT人，冇調查過Bridgefy 嘅背景<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n不分化，不割蓆！"},{"pid":"69813817d0a8e5164f531c78e5a7f367dc9cfaf8","tid":1634767,"uid":204615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply